    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>Welcome to my world.This is my very first post.<br>先随便写几句，折腾了两天hexo配合github搭建博客成功，距离大大绚丽的页面还有好远。<br>建博客的过程中，遇到了好多问题，看教程的时候仿佛大家都水到渠成，只有我和成功之间隔着千山万水。<br>ORZ记录一下遇到的问题和解决方法.<br><a id="more"></a> </p><h2 id="Let’s-start"><a href="#Let’s-start" class="headerlink" title="Let’s start!!!"></a>Let’s start!!!</h2><p>可以边听边看哦！<br>        <div id="aplayer-jtuiKPFf" class="aplayer aplayer-tag-marker" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">            <pre class="aplayer-lrc-content"></pre>        </div>        <script>          var ap = new APlayer({            element: document.getElementById("aplayer-jtuiKPFf"),            narrow: false,            autoplay: false,            showlrc: false,            music: {              title: "Hit and Run",              author: "Lolo",              url: "https://link.hhtjim.com/163/28987151.mp3",              pic: "https://i.loli.net/2019/05/09/5cd41d6fa31f5.jpg",              lrc: ""            }          });          window.aplayers || (window.aplayers = []);          window.aplayers.push(ap);        </script></p><h3 id="修改hosts访问google"><a href="#修改hosts访问google" class="headerlink" title="修改hosts访问google"></a>修改hosts访问google</h3><p>首先是ipconfig/flushdns 无法使用，解决方法<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/hi_boy_/article/details/78059189" target="_blank" rel="noopener">设置path</a></p><h3 id="安装node-js和git"><a href="#安装node-js和git" class="headerlink" title="安装node.js和git"></a>安装node.js和git</h3><div class="note default"><p>default</p></div><h3 id="安装hexo"><a href="#安装hexo" class="headerlink" title="安装hexo"></a>安装hexo</h3><p>报错：local hexo not found in xxx:<br>在网上各种搜索都没有解决问题，删除项目中的package.json,执行npm init生成新的package.json替换，虽然不再报错，但是出现了新问题，返回usage信息，hexo命令干脆不能用了，倒腾一晚上，最后考虑是环境变量问题。<br>第二天重装node.js确认，问题是node.js版本过低所致。</p><h3 id="部署到github"><a href="#部署到github" class="headerlink" title="部署到github"></a>部署到github</h3><p>报错：could not read from remote repository<br>经过检查发现是github项目名称写错</p><h3 id="中文乱码"><a href="#中文乱码" class="headerlink" title="中文乱码"></a>中文乱码</h3><p>多半是编码问题，换个编码方式编辑。换为UTF-8编码方式，成功解决。</p><h3 id="如何更新博客"><a href="#如何更新博客" class="headerlink" title="如何更新博客"></a>如何更新博客</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new <span class="string">"My New Post"</span></span><br><span class="line">$ hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo g -d</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="网易云音乐产生外部链接"><a href="#网易云音乐产生外部链接" class="headerlink" title="网易云音乐产生外部链接"></a>网易云音乐产生外部链接</h3><p><a href="http://link.hhtjim.com/163/xxx.mps" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://link.hhtjim.com/163/xxx.mps</a> 将歌曲链接的对应id替换xxx位置即可</p><hr>]]></content>
    
